## -- Access controls

PropDef:
  @QName:
    ManakaiDOM:isForInternal
  @dataType:
    dis:Boolean
  @Description:
    @@lang:en
    @@@:
      Whether the subject resource is prepared for the internal use.  
      In other word, the subject resource is a public member or 
      a private member.

## -- Status

PropDef:
  @QName: isDeprecated
  @dataType:
    dis:Boolean
  @Description:
    @@lang:en
    @@@:
      Whether the use of the subject resource is deprecated or not. 

PropDef:
  @QName: alt
  @dataType:
    dis:TFQNames
  @Description:
    @@lang:en
    @@@:
      Another resource the subject resource is deprecated in favor of. 
      \
      This property is specified as a child element of 
      <Q::isDeprecated> property element.

